---
syntax: bash
tags: [ file-manager ]
---

# Launch yazi (with cd-on-exit wrapper)
y

# Navigation
# j/k        Move down/up
# h/l        Parent dir / Enter dir
# gg/G       Top / Bottom
# /          Search

# File operations
# o          Open file
# a          Create file
# r          Rename
# d          Trash
# D          Permanently delete
# y          Yank (copy)
# x          Cut
# p          Paste
# .          Toggle hidden files

# Selection
# Space      Select current
# v          Visual mode (select range)
# V          Inverse selection

# Tabs
# t          New tab
# 1-9        Switch to tab N
# Ctrl+c     Close tab

# Other
# q          Quit
# ~          Help
# z          Jump (fzf)
# Z          Jump (zoxide)
